      <h2  style="text-align: center; color: #0075b4;font-family: Source Sans Pro,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif">Meet Our Team</h2>
      <br>
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-lg-3">
            <img class="img-fluid rounded" src="https://cdn.sotercares.com/images/troy-headshot.jpg" alt="" style="max-height: 300px">
